# rules.dropboxignore — keep session/cache junk out of a Dropbox-synced replication package.
# Complements (does NOT replace) .gitignore. Copy to the package root when the project syncs via Dropbox.
# Adapted from Yusaku Horiuchi's replication-package-guide (R) + Python/general additions.

# R / RStudio local + session files
**/.Rproj.user/
**/.Rhistory
**/.RData
**/.Ruserdata
**/Rplots.pdf
**/renv/library/
**/renv/staging/

# Python caches + envs
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.ipynb_checkpoints/
**/.venv/
**/.uv-cache/

# generic build/cache leftovers
**/*_cache/
**/*_files/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/

# OS + temp files
**/.DS_Store
**/*.tmp
**/*.temp
**/*.bak
